 <H1>Technical Basis</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Treat architecture as set of interacting processes
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>for both components and connectors
<LI>behavior described using a form of CSP specification (Wright)
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Specify a reconfiguration program, which handles all architectural reconfigurations
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>uses primitive operators to create/delete/attach components and connectors
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Components and connectors raise control events 
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>explicitly identifies places where reconfiguration may occur</UL></UL></P>
